Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:56.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1426,492)}牛油果公寓区\N疗养社区
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.78,0:00:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  牛油果公寓区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, Avocondo Acres
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的顶级疗养社区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's premier retirement community
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这能找到哈罗德和玛格丽特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where we find Harold and Margaret
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这对父母诞下了全海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the parents of the ocean's
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最不寻常的多细胞生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,most exceptional multicellular organism
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈罗德  你闻到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harold, did you smell that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It smells like something
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.93,0:01:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rotting
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's begun
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.27,0:01:23.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好马上逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:23.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We better run
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.86,0:01:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都跟人说了要用柠檬汁擦房子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tell people to rub their homes with lemon juice
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再用塑料包起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and wrap it in plastic
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他们有听我话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But do they listen?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈罗德  我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Harold, what will we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.78,0:01:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只能再种一个新家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll just have to grow a new home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这期间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And in the meantime
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以跟儿子一块住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can stay with our son
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快找掩护  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take cover, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch this
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跳上跳下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I jump up and down
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汽水瓶盖就会爆开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The soda bottles pop their corks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.05,0:02:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后危险万分带我整间房到处冲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and send me careening dangerously around the room
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很有可能活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may not survive
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.19,0:02:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.56,0:02:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸爸好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your house?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.77,0:02:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我一块住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然可以的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, of course you can
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.32,0:02:24.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸妈要第一次来我们家住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad are coming over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:24.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to stay at our place for the very first time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚想到点事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just thought of something
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爸妈有好些日子没见我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My parents haven't seen me in a while
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可能会期望看到儿子变得更加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll be expecting their son to be a little more
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  成年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, adult--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大人  成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,grown-up, mature--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你再看看我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And look at this place
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又脏又乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a filthy mess
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peek-a-boo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干净
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好干净
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So clean
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.91,0:03:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须别再这么碰面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We gotta stop meeting like this
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You almost done?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会不会很有意思呢  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't this be fun, dear?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟儿子那样的新潮都市年轻人一块
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hanging out with a hip, young urbanite like our boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们真的特别需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can really use
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往内心注入年轻精神  活力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an injection of youthful spirit, vitality
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.72,0:03:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甚至是莽撞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and dare I say, recklessness
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mater, Pater
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是天大的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is truly a pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't you entrer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,724)}进去之后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今天要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what are we gonna do today?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要进城里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to hit the town
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我冒昧写了一份活动日程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have taken the liberty of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,writing up an agenda of activities
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.47,0:04:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面内容对于我们大人都十分刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I know all of us adults will find most stimulating
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先要在这附近散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll begin with a leisurely walk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:23.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about the neighborhood
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,共同评价别人家的草坪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so we can critique other people's lawns
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After that--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讨论税款  政治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,conversations about taxes, politics
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1200,344)}政治             税款\N所有东西烂透了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有现在的事物有多么大不如前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and how things aren't nearly as good as they used to be
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后早早吃一顿晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then an early-bird dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午四点以睡觉结束这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we'll top it off with bedtime at 4:00 pm
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是儿子  这不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But son, this isn't--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以的  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, son
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是你客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're your guests
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午四点钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,4:00 in the afternoon
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点热牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some warm milk
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.30,0:04:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有舒缓的啧啧牢骚声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the soothing sounds of disapproval
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以帮你们快快入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to whisk you off to your slumbers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都被禁足了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are so grounded
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能不要再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you puh-lease stop that confounded racket?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有大人还想在里面睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some grown-ups are trying to sleep in here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  我亲爱的蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, my dear gastropod
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玛格丽特  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Margaret, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕儿子已经变成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid our son has become
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  老古板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, a fuddy duddy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用词可能不是很恰当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon my language
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I was gonna say
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很失望  压抑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"bummer, a downer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还特别乏味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a total drag"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱要不要一起溜出去找点乐子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say we sneak out and have some fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老早就想这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Way ahead of you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where have you two been?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经晚上八点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is 8:00 at night
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我担心得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was worried sick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是在找点乐子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were just having a little fun
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个表现得跟小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're both acting like children
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.22,0:06:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现得跟个方正老古板一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're acting like a square
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来就方正
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am square
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我已经下定决心要表现成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I've already committed to acting mature
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你们喜不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,whether you like it or not
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行吧  成熟先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Mature
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在倒也得来找点乐子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time for you to have some fun
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你喜不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,whether you like it or not
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村狂欢夜开始了  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Bikini Bottom after dark, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对疯得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be wild
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上啊  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on, son
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟她一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Join her
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须给我去  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is an order, son
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝刀未老
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still got it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  扫兴鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, killjoy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别老这么扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a party pooper
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快扔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在太幼稚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is so childish
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is going--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蒙面摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Masked luchador wrestling
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,年少无知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How juvenile
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess this is all right
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该也疯不到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be too wild
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,光坐在这看着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just sitting here, watching
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不是来这光看的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not here to watch
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是来摔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to wrestle
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,组合摔跤时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's tag team time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,828)}组合摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,828)}时间
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.93,0:07:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大恶魔对战爸妈组合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Los Diablos vs Madre y Padre
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好小子  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Atta boy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们支持你  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're rooting for you, kiddo
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一轮比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For our next bout
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.88,0:08:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死神对战花生袋先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's El Muerte vs Señor Peanuts Bag
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No más
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好不好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, wasn't that fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个戴着花生袋的哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd that peanut bag guy go?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热狗要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How 'bout a hot dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:31.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(1170,560)}24{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}小时轮滑场
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never even knew
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村有家24小时营业的轮滑场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there was a 24-hour roller rink in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.38,0:09:36.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计在轮滑场里慢慢滑也疯不到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess skating slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:36.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,around and around a roller rink isn't so wild
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,场里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rink?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要溜遍全城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're skating through town
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个能不能表现成熟点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you two please act your age?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please stop
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you slow down?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:07.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786,874)}手套乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算我求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想给你们留下好印象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to impress you two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在你们面前当个成熟大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by showing you what a mature adult I've become
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你们偏不  净想着疯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But no, you wanted wild
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想疯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want wild?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就给你们瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wild
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子睡着了  累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boy's asleep, all tuckered out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们新种的牛油果公寓应该快熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, our new avocondo should be ripe right now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只能先跟我们住一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll have to stay with us
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等菠萝屋重新长出来再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until he can regrow his pineapple
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.19,0:11:18.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:18.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他何时才会真正成长成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when he'll really grow up and be mature
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿不会太早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopefully not too soon
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吗  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I right dear?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花生袋先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Señor Peanuts Bag
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要伤害赔偿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want satisfaction
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花生也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or peanuts
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我比较想吃花生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd rather peanuts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.67,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFA3&}黄 道
