Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,962)}影片开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:56.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,268)}海中安全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:56.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,918)}安全驾驶教育影片
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位学员大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, student drivers
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.41,0:12:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Mrs. Penelope Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按照法院的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and as per the court order
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.02,0:12:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会在这部教育影片中担任教练
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will be your driving instructor in this education film
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.32,0:12:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要记牢138条简简单单的交规
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By remembering these 138 simple rules of the road
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们大家自然就能心领神会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every one of you will know all that you need
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.71,0:12:19.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考到驾照的必备知识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:19.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get your very own boating license
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1580,428)}墙
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连我都会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,408)}五点预查
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是好司机先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we have Mr. Good Driver
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在把船发动之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Before starting the vehicle
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.97,0:12:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为确保安全  他会检查船的五个区域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he always inspects five areas of his boat for safety
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他检查了轮胎浮力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He checks his tire buoyancy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.57,0:12:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确保螺旋桨润滑充分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ensures his propeller is properly oiled
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确认船上汽笛正常运作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Confirms his boat horn is functioning
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,复查信号旗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reviews his signals
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And most importantly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.77,0:12:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他系好了安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he fastens his seat belt
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另外的这位是差司机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here we have a bad driver
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.27,0:13:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我称之为  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or what I refer to as a "SpongeBob"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,检查胎压
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check tire pressure
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,润滑螺旋桨  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oil propeller, check
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,检查汽笛  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check horn, check
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of the way
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,检查信号旗  完完成成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check signals, checkerino
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seat belt
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Belted
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在能领驾照了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get my license now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(952,920)}不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,456)}上路
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在进入第二课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to our second lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开船上路时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As he begins his journey
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好司机先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Good Driver
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.48,0:13:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都会仔细观察左右来船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,makes sure to watch carefully for oncoming boats
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有等前方没有来船了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only when the road is clear
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.82,0:13:57.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他才会加速驶入道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:57.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,does he accelerate into traffic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1304,880)}美味热狗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能领驾照了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get my license now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(924,840)}不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,442)}注意行人
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三课
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lesson three
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,路上会有多种不同的行人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are several types of pedestrians
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.21,0:14:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是好司机先生都会留意观察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Good Driver always keeps careful watch
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前面出现了灵巧的小老太太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we have the cunning little, old lady
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.27,0:14:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有坐着童车的咿咿呀呀小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the babbling baby in a buggy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,普普通通的水果摊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The common fruit vendor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然  前面还有几个工人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And naturally, we see some workmen
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搬着一大块玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,carrying a large pane of glass
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好老套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How cliché
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.07,0:15:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好司机先生也许自认为能放松警惕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Good Driver may think he can let his guard down
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但还有一位行人正等着攻其不备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but there's still one pedestrian waiting to strike
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.28,0:15:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稀有物种  恼人海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rare Poriferous Aggravatus
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:14.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,868)}恼人海绵
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.34,0:15:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俗称  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,commonly known as a SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能领驾照了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get my license now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,886)}胶卷丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,628)}导航
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第29课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lesson 29
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.02,0:15:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好司机先生一定要按交通标识行船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Good Driver must obey various road signs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面是一些例子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here are just a few
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意减速带
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speed bumps
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前方玩耍儿童慢行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slow children at play
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候  连好司机先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, even Mr. Good Driver
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都有可能被方向弄迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,may be overwhelmed with directions
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.40,0:16:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾驶时不得看地图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never read a road map while driving
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有海绵宝宝会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's something only a SpongeBob would do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:52.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,474)}正确的乘员礼节
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第53课
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lesson 53
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全驾驶同样意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good driving also means
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.27,0:16:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖乖当好乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,being a good passenger--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不害司机分心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,never distract your driver
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天要领到驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get my license today
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师说影片拍完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff said, at the end of the film
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就有驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会领到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get it all right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.15,0:17:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不在后座对司机指手画脚同样重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's also important not to be a backseat driver
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以坐在后座开船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can drive from the back seat?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.62,0:17:20.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:20.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我快疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're driving me crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后  作为乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, as a passenger
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不能随意玩弄中控
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you must never play with the boat's control console
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来放点音乐听听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get some tunes going here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然来开空调吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How 'bout some AC?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too cold
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.45,0:17:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me help you with that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.65,0:18:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.93,0:18:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,624)}路怒症
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第54课
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lesson 54
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.81,0:18:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连好司机先生都很有可能忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even Mr. Good Driver may be tempted
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对同行的司机大发雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to take out his anger on a fellow motorist
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这样的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In times like these
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要记住一个简单的词
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,remember one simple word--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,720)}怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450,820)}放松
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,820)}再
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1084,820)}绕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1732,820)}到别处
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个我会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know this one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你放松  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me help you relax, friend
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,深深吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just breathe in
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再呼出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要喝杯放松心情的海草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, how about a relaxing cup of kelp tea?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是清爽宜人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Refreshing, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来扫沙子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's rake some sand
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  放松
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, relaxed
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要绕到别处了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time to go elsewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破烂投影仪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This darn projector--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一到最精彩的部分就坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just when we were getting to the good part
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让好学生来帮你继续
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let a good noodle handle that for you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好演特写镜头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready for my close-up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来影片放不完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we can't finish the film
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可  可要是影片放不完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B--b--but if we can't finish the film
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,课就上不完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can't finish class
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是上不完课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if we can't finish class
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.57,0:20:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就领不到驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then I can't get my license
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我亲自来演完影片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll finish the film myself
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是万众期待的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, the moment you've all been waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,296)}驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,784)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝的驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's boating license
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.12,0:20:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝是个极具模范意义的司机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob was such an exemplary driver
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.49,0:20:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puh-lease
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.62,0:20:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,市政厅为了纪念他  举办了特别仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That a special ceremony was held
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in his honor at city hall
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:21:00.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,266)}市政厅
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,此时此刻  梦想成真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a dream come true
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.72,0:21:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师坚信他配得上脚下的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff had deemed him worthy of the road
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他最终领到了耀眼的  真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He finally had a dazzling, genuine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实物大小的驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,full-sized boating license
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满怀着高超的驾驶技术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, imbued with the power of good driving
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝向混乱世界中的人民们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob brought peace to the people
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带来了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of this troubled world
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他把蟹黄堡送给了饥民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He delivered Krabby Patties to the hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,制止了违法小罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He de-escalated petty crime
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.42,0:21:30.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还阻止了冰盖融化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:30.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he even kept the ice cap from melting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.31,0:21:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  大家此时此刻最爱海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, everyone loved SpongeBob more than ever
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他成功领到了驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now that he had his boating license
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.75,0:21:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家深深爱着他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They all loved him so much
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.51,0:21:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is quite enough
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下周继续上内容正常的课
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll resume the correct lesson next week
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下课
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Class is dismissed
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.72,0:21:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把今天学到的知识记牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just remember what you learned today
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.07,0:21:58.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准再胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:58.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and no more of this nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mrs. Puff
